---
title: Porchetta Inspired Sammie with Sautéed and Potato Wedges
description: Watch as we transform the humble ham steak into a porchetta-inspired sammie! Spicy lemon aioli, braised greens, and crispy onions bring it all up a notch, while classic potato wedges make delicious dippers!
